# These are configured in Supabase, not in .env
# Just enable Google provider in Supabase dashboard

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NOTES
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. All NEXT_PUBLIC_ variables are exposed to the browser
# 2. Never expose secret keys (SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, YOCO_SECRET_KEY, YOCO_WEBHOOK_SECRET, RESEND_API_KEY)
# 3. Use test/sandbox credentials for development
# 4. Update NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL when deploying to production
# 5. Run all SQL scripts in /scripts folder before starting the app
